  "title": "HappyGhastUtils",
  "description": "HappyGhastUtils is a quality of life utility mod for the Happy Ghast.",
  "body": "![Happy Ghast Utils](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fweigel-dev/HappyGhastUtils/refs/heads/main/README/minecraft_title.png)\n\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/fweigel-dev/HappyGhastUtils\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fweigel-dev/HappyGhastUtils/refs/heads/main/README/github_icon_bg.png\" alt=\"GitHub\" style=\"margin: 5px 10px;\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/happyghastutils\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fweigel-dev/HappyGhastUtils/refs/heads/main/README/modrinth_icon_bg.png\" alt=\"Modrinth\" style=\"margin: 5px 10px;\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/happyghastutils\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fweigel-dev/HappyGhastUtils/refs/heads/main/README/curseforge_icon_bg.png\" alt=\"CurseForge\" style=\"margin: 5px 10px;\"></a>\n</p>\n\n<div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 40px 0;\">\n  <div>\n    <h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700;\">Supported Versions:</h3>\n    <img width=\"165\" height=\"84\" alt=\"Minecraft 26.1\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fweigel-dev/HappyGhastUtils/refs/heads/main/README/26.1.png\"/>\n    <img width=\"165\" height=\"84\" alt=\"Minecraft 26.2\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fweigel-dev/HappyGhastUtils/refs/heads/main/README/26.2.png\"/>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\nHappy Ghast Utils is a client-side Fabric mod that enhances the Happy Ghast experience in Minecraft.\n\n## Features\n\n### Hydration Indicator\n\nSee the hydration level of Dried Ghasts.\n\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fweigel-dev/HappyGhastUtils/refs/heads/main/README/hydration_indicator.png\" width=\"480\" style=\"border-radius: 10px\"/>\n\n---\n\n### Baby Timer\n\nA countdown timer above every Ghastling showing the time remaining until it grows into a Happy Ghast.\n\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fweigel-dev/HappyGhastUtils/refs/heads/main/README/baby_timer.png\" width=\"600\" style=\"border-radius: 10px\"/>\n\n---\n\n### Navigation & Autopilot\n\nSet a destination by entering X, Y, Z coordinates, the autopilot will navigate you to the target.\n\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fweigel-dev/HappyGhastUtils/refs/heads/main/README/navigation.gif\" width=\"600\" style=\"border-radius: 10px\"/>\n\n---\n\n### Sound Volume Control\n\nAdjust the volume of Happy Ghast and Ghastling sounds independently of the main game volume.\n\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fweigel-dev/HappyGhastUtils/refs/heads/main/README/settings.png\" width=\"600\" style=\"border-radius: 10px\"/>\n",
